{
  "title": "Tangy Springy Uruguayan Cheese Fried Rice",
  "description": "A satvik friendly Uruguayan dish featuring liquid cheese and a blend of spices, this tangy springy cheese fried rice is perfect for a romantic dinner",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
